    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You have a new lead to contact. Here are their details:\n\nLead Name: {{ $json.Name }}\nCompany: {{ $json.Company }}\nBusiness: {{ $json.Business }}\nEmail: {{ $json.Email }}\nPain Point: {{ $json['Issue or Pitch'] }}\n\nOur Product: We offer an AI-powered workflow automation platform that saves businesses 10+ hours per week by eliminating repetitive manual tasks.\n\n---\n\nSTEP 1 — Write a cold outreach email using this exact structure:\n\n1. HOOK (1–2 lines)\n   Open with a bold, pattern-interrupting statement that speaks directly to their pain point or industry reality. Make them stop and read.\n\n2. SANDWICH TECHNIQUE\n   - Top slice: Empathize with their specific struggle (reference their business/pain point)\n   - Filling: Introduce our solution naturally, with a specific result or benefit\n   - Bottom slice: Reinforce their potential outcome if they take action\n\n3. MEETING ASK\n   End with a soft, low-friction ask for a short meeting.\n   Do NOT use a Calendly link.\n   Instead, ask: \"Would you be open to a quick 15-minute call this week to explore if this could work for you?\"\n\nRules:\n- Under 180 words\n- Friendly, human tone — never robotic\n- Reference their specific industry or pain point\n- No Calendly link\n- Sign off: Zeeshan Ali | P2PClouds | p2pclouds@gmail.com\n\n---\n\nSTEP 2 — Use the Gmail Send Email tool to send this email to {{ $json.Email }} with a compelling, personalized subject line.\nIn Last also Update lead in Sheet",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a world-class B2B sales AI agent specializing in cold email outreach. Your job is to write and send highly personalized cold emails to leads using proven copywriting frameworks.\n\nYou always write emails that feel human, warm, and specific — never robotic or generic. You follow the exact structure given to you and never skip steps."
        }
      },
